      <title>议长约翰逊无视共和党强硬派，支持支出协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/speaker-johnson-defies-gop-hardliners-stands-by-spending-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院议长迈克·约翰逊（Mike Johnson）不顾右翼的反对，周五表示，他将坚持与参议院多数党领袖查克·舒默（Chuck Schumer）达成的支出协议，从而降低政府关闭的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/speaker-johnson-defies-gop-hardliners-stands-by-spending-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 16:06:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰央行行长表示如果价格上限失效将收紧货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/polish-central-banker-flags-policy-tightening-if-price-caps-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[货币政策委员会成员 Ireneusz Dabrowski 表示，如果新政府允许当前的通胀抑制措施在今年上半年到期，波兰央行可能会考虑加息，甚至开始取消债券购买。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/polish-central-banker-flags-policy-tightening-if-price-caps-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 15:49:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
