    <item>
      <title>胡塞武装与美国的对决是伊朗“抵抗轴心”的分水岭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/yemen-airstrikes-iran-sees-payoff-from-investment-in-axis-of-resistance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旨在威吓也门胡塞武装分子的空袭正在使美国及其盟友与伊朗支持的运动展开对立，该运动在三个月前抓住以色列与哈马斯的战争后，意识到自己的时刻已经到来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/yemen-airstrikes-iran-sees-payoff-from-investment-in-axis-of-resistance</guid>
